name: Catless Icekating
description:
Catless Iceskating

In a world full of cats and socks all this nameless cat wants to do is... ice skating and vibe to the groove.

Controls

W | A | D | S -> Play on Keyboard

∆ | O | ▢ | X-> Play on Controller

F11 -> Fullscreen

Credits

Game Made By:

Eduardo Barrancos -> Programming

Tiago Martins -> Art

Satie - Gymnopedie no1 (music)

This game was made for an internal game jam of Game Dev Técnico

The Game Lasts 1:12 Minutes. Have fun and Merry Christmas!
